data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","output_index":1,"item_id":"msg_tmp_v03lyel88p","content_index":0,"text":"Anthropic's most recent product launch is **Claude 2.1**, announced on **November 21, 2023**. This version introduces several significant improvements, including:\n\n1. **200,000 Token Context Window**: This feature allows Claude 2.1 to process and analyze large amounts of text, enabling it to summarize lengthy documents, perform question-and-answer tasks over extensive content, and more. This is an industry-leading capability that allows users to relay up to 150,000 words or over 500 pages of material to the model in a single interaction.\n\n2. **Reduced Hallucination Rates**: Claude 2.1 has achieved a **2x decrease in false statements** compared to its predecessor, enhancing its reliability for enterprise applications.\n\n3. **Beta Feature: Tool Use**: This allows Claude to integrate with user-defined processes and APIs, expanding its versatility in real-world applications by enabling it to perform specific tasks such as calculations or data retrieval from external databases.\n\n4. **Improvements in Accuracy and Comprehension**: The model has seen enhancements in its ability to comprehend and summarize complex information, making it suitable for sensitive tasks such as legal and financial document analysis.\n\nThese updates aim to make Claude 2.1 more effective and user-friendly for businesses across various industries. For more details, you can read the official announcement on Anthropic's website [here](https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-2-1).","logprobs":[],"sequence_number":308}

